sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as RagasEvaluatorInline<br/>(in-process)
    participant Remote as RagasEvaluatorRemote<br/>(in-process)
    participant DatasetIO as DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Inference as Inference API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Backend as Ollama/vLLM<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pod<br/>(container)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation

    Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS->>Inline: Dispatch to inline provider
    Inline->>DatasetIO: Fetch dataset (in-process)
    DatasetIO-->>Inline: Dataset rows
    Inline->>Inference: LLM completions via<br/>LlamaStackInlineLLM wrapper
    Inference->>Backend: HTTP/11434 plaintext
    Backend-->>Inference: LLM response
    Inference-->>Inline: Completion result
    Inline->>Inference: Embeddings via<br/>LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings wrapper
    Inference->>Backend: HTTP/11434 plaintext
    Backend-->>Inference: Embedding vectors
    Inference-->>Inline: Embedding result
    Note over Inline: Ragas evaluate()<br/>answer_relevancy, faithfulness,<br/>context_precision, context_recall
    Inline-->>LLS: Evaluation results
    LLS-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)

    Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS->>Remote: Dispatch to remote provider
    Remote->>KFP: Submit pipeline run<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OpenShift)
    KFP-->>Remote: Pipeline run ID

    Note over Client,Remote: Client polls with /alpha/eval/job_status

    KFP->>KFPPod: Create retrieve_data pod
    KFPPod->>LLS: GET dataset<br/>HTTP/8321 No Auth
    LLS-->>KFPPod: Dataset (JSONL)

    KFP->>KFPPod: Create run_ragas pod
    KFPPod->>LLS: POST inference/embeddings<br/>HTTP/8321 via RemoteLLM/RemoteEmbeddings
    LLS->>Backend: HTTP/11434 plaintext
    Backend-->>LLS: LLM/Embedding response
    LLS-->>KFPPod: Results
    Note over KFPPod: Ragas evaluate()
    KFPPod->>S3: Write results<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (env vars from Secret)

    Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job_result<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    Remote->>S3: Read results<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (via s3fs)
    S3-->>Remote: Evaluation results JSON
    Remote-->>LLS: Parsed results
    LLS-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
